{"type":null,"faqId":22432,"title":"画面不满屏、比例失调或超出屏幕显示区域怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in 0.59097224in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.4861111in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.15763889in;margin-left:0.15763889in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:0.35416666in;margin-top:0.083333336in;margin-bottom:0.090277776in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><a name=\"screen_1_sec5_p1\"></a><span>可能是显示区域的设置有问题，请进入华为盒子“</span><span class=\"s2\">设置 &gt; 显示 &gt; 显示区域</span><span>”，按遥控器方向键</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=74453\" style=\"width:0.46180555in;height:0.41597223in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，调整画面的显示区域。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=74454\" style=\"width:4.329861in;height:2.4340277in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span>可能是华为盒子的屏幕比例与电视机不一致。请进入华为盒子“</span><span class=\"s2\">设置 &gt; 播放 &gt; 屏幕比例</span><span>”，传统电视请设置为 4:3，高清电视请设置为 16:9。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=74455\" style=\"width:4.329861in;height:2.4333334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">&gt;  </span><span>电视机本身的显示区域有问题，请根据实际显示效果。调整电视机的显示区域。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=74456\" style=\"width:0.17847222in;height:0.19722222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span>部分视频本身为固定的长宽比，此时屏幕显示黑边，属于正常现象。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":247,"faqType":"显示","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"6312","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1428628514000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M330","visitedTimes":54,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"M330,MediaQ M330,华为盒子,满屏,比例失调","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}